WEBVTT

00:03:59.583 --> 00:04:01.727
sodir bo'ladigan o'zgarishlar to'plamisiz:

00:04:01.727 --> 00:04:05.420
sizning tanangiz, ongingiz, hislaringiz,
hayotiy sharoitlaringiz va hattoki

00:04:05.420 --> 00:04:11.628
g'alati odatlaringiz doimo o'zgarib 
turadi, ammo hayratlanarlisi shundaki,

00:04:11.628 --> 00:04:16.629
ba'zan esa mantiqqa zid ravishda 
siz o'zgarishsiz qolmoqdasiz.

00:04:16.629 --> 00:04:19.074
Shuning uchun "Men o'zi kimman?" degan 
savolga

00:04:19.074 --> 00:04:24.431
javob berish juda qiyin.
Bunga javob berish uchun, sizga

00:04:24.431 --> 00:04:25.875
oldin o'tgan ko'plab buyuk

00:04:25.875 --> 00:04:28.445
mutafakkirlarga o'xshab falsafiy 
paradoksning tubsiz

00:04:28.445 --> 00:04:33.897
okeaniga sho'ng'ish kerak bo'ladi. Lekin, 
siz oddiy javob berishingiz ham mumkin: